A6%2582%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E9%2581%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8&h=2e867625\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210325/s00001/1616658642013/%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%BA%AD%E8%A3%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E8%80%85%E4%BA%A6%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%A5%E7%BD%AA-%E3%80%8C%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8D%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月28日反修例示威者和警方在上環爆發衝突，一對健身公司東主夫婦和16歲少女被控暴動罪，至去年7月經審訊後被裁定罪名不成立。律政司後來要求上訴庭釐清，「共同犯案」（joint enterprise）的概念可否套用非法集結和暴動罪的案件中。上訴庭今（25日）頒下判辭，裁定有關概念適用於《公安條例》的非法集結和暴動罪，即不在犯案現場的人同樣有可能入罪。<br />\n<br />\n呢條濕鳩律政司有冇搞撚錯?<br />\n即係以後唔出街都會被charge暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人你哋仲等乜能嘢？仲唔走 等拉呀?!"},{"pid":"74986afdf39a3231b7043994b3ec715cf9165414","tid":2461081,"uid":291750,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:20:01.000Z","msg":"CLS係屋企食花生又暴動！"},{"pid":"97b17f1524970769203b497f1e7e865ded122f95","tid":2461081,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:21:53.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣即係全香港7百萬人都有暴動罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31934f9fca4668eb68e97fea637caa72ecc950ab","tid":2461081,"uid":134227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />預撚左<br />\n早走早著"},{"pid":"1282c5aa6b3d7417096560004c52bc4de452ef59","tid":2461081,"uid":179409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"佢係有心推翻你成套普通法<br />\n不斷僭建一堆反人權同有罪假定嘅條文入去<br />\n然後同你講依法辦事<br />\n用人治扮法治"},{"pid":"a20ac42da5a227472ca39fa91d0b7111e8360fe7","tid":2461081,"uid":8566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"即係大家屋企做冷氣軍師睇live <br />\n<br />\n但只要有通風報信都拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as